# Rename/copy this file to:  .dev.vars   (same folder as wrangler.toml). Restart Wrangler after edits.
# From repo root:
#   npm run dev
# Without AUDIT_UPSTREAM_URL + AUDIT_UPSTREAM_TOKEN uncommented here, /api/v1/audit-remote/* returns 503 — use Offline demo or set both vars.
# Uses wrangler.toml (dist + ./functions).
#
# Cloudflare production: set the same name in Pages → Settings → Environment variables.

NVIDIA_API_KEY=replace_with_your_nvapi_token

# Audit AI → Hugging Face (same-origin proxy; secrets stay in Wrangler / Pages — never in browser)
# AUDIT_UPSTREAM_URL=https://YOUR_USER-YOUR_SPACE.hf.space
# AUDIT_UPSTREAM_TOKEN=same_as_AUDIT_API_SECRET_on_hf_space
#
# Private Space (HF gateway expects hf_* read token on Authorization):
# AUDIT_HF_READ_TOKEN=hf_xxxxxxxx
# When set, Wrangler sends Authorization: Bearer hf_* and X-Audit-Secret: Bearer <AUDIT_UPSTREAM_TOKEN>
#
# Local UI test: npm run dev → http://127.0.0.1:8788 then in browser console:
#   localStorage.setItem('mustalih_hf_proxy','1'); location.reload();
